    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty bleak take lol. isn't it more like the UN is just limited by how much power individual countries actually want to give up? like, is the failure really the UN itself, or is it just how the world works? could you expand a bit on the arguments that say the UN is still working as intended?",
